-12-09T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"係，人類會大滅絕<br />\n岩唔岩聽？"},{"pid":"de7cb1b3f682e54a4e6f99d5b0dca477b74eb525","tid":2314422,"uid":24045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"想留低就死都唔好打疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082aa077d5bb450512f645b6d656d65fa56aab13","tid":2314422,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"阿南德認為，全球將在今年12月20日再度迎來大災難，並持續至2021年3月21日，他預計這有可能是疫情二度大流行，也可能是出現超級細菌（superbugs）。"},{"pid":"59d1f984484bcdaa0e1621f9dc6a042d04e61394","tid":2314422,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bed40a18aa69b6b88820eb5bfc517722e20836bd","tid":2314422,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"如果打完中國疫苗不育 世界人口應該會大幅減少<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"#中共<br />\n#東突<br />\n#打針<br />\n#絕育"},{"pid":"8a1b1aef8e3bbd1c4cb6c62b751766cdcfc08be7","tid":2314422,"uid":297468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"純粹覺得<br />\n你問得呢d問題<br />\n好似唔知自己細個打過幾多枝疫苗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e16968231506354d0e35d3bc76401b55b49986","tid":2314422,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"未證明到Pfizer vaccine對fertility冇壞影響<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://healthimpactnews.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/12/Information_for_healthcare_professionals.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealthimpactnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2020%2F12%2FInformation_for_healthcare_professionals.pdf&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2qzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=46ff9aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://healthimpactnews.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/12/Information_for_healthcare_professionals.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n4.6 Fertility, pregnancy and lactation<br />\n<br />\nPregnancy<br />\nThere are no or limited amount of data from the use of COVID-19 mRNA Vaccine BNT162b2. Animal reproductive toxicity studies have not been completed. COVID-19 mRNA Vaccine BNT162b2 is not recommended during pregnancy. For women of childbearing age, pregnancy should be excluded before vaccination. In addition, women of childbearing age should be advised to avoid pregnancy for at least 2 months after their second dose.<br />\n<br />\nBreast-feeding<br />\nIt is unknown whether COVID-19 mRNA Vaccine BNT162b2 is excreted in human milk. A risk to the newborns/infants cannot be excluded. COVID-19 mRNA Vaccine BNT162b2 should not be used during breast-feeding.<br />\n<br />\nFertility<br />\nIt is unknown whether COVID-19 mRNA Vaccine BNT162b2 has an impact on fertility."},{"pid":"f980555fa19a59bc4175986fa0bc37d6a1f29f31","tid":2314422,"uid":382841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"疫苗對付唔到變種病毒<br />\n打黎只係為藥廠埋單<br />\n唔打好過打"}]}